# Liabilities Deposits Transaction At Call Or On Demand Amount

## identifier
de7490

## type
float

## definition
This is the value of deposits held at the relevant date redeemable or withdrawable by depositors from the reporting party on demand or within 24 hours, and from which the reporting party is able to make payments to parties other than the account holder.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=credit
- name=Liabilities.Deposits.TransactionAtCallOrOnDemand.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpo/bafpo6.02.06
- period=instant
